items.headline: Welcome to The Office Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to The Office Wiki, also known as Dunderpedia, the wiki all about the world of American sitcom called The Office. It is based on the British series of the same name and ran for nine seasons, until 2013. Just because the show is over doesn't mean there's nothing left to do, though. Join us and share your knowledge and passion for The Office so we can be a complete encyclopedia for all things The Office. After all, this is a wiki that anyone can edit, including you!
